{"tid":307144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"59歲設計師鄧達智與同性醫生密友傳婚訊","createTime":"2017-07-03T06:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T06:35:36.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0df28dbbb3272227f3e35afc18c2fe3dcd7a5e","tid":307144,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"59歲設計師鄧達智與同性醫生密友傳婚訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170703/s00007/46dbf92e9f63399ac7f6c9ef27a98540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170703%2Fs00007%2F46dbf92e9f63399ac7f6c9ef27a98540.jpg&h=7ba46e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n59歲本地著名設計師鄧達智（William）一直未有承認出櫃，但近年他不時在社交網上分享與同性醫生密友Clement Chan的生活及旅行照，同時今日更傳出鄧達智於上月28日結婚的消息，當時在幾位好友見證下，兩人並交換戒指及祝酒，但暫時仍未聯絡得上William，未由他親自證實此消息。 <br />\nWilliam在Facebook內不時上載與醫生密友Clement Chan的大頭合照及旅行照片，曾一齊赴日浸溫泉。若果William結婚消息屬實，他是繼王賢誌與男友Kevin，盧凱彤與攝影師女友余靜萍之後，出櫃結婚的本地著名時尚圈名人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170703/s00007/1499060615695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170703%2Fs00007%2F1499060615695&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=10bb86a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170703%2Fs00007%2F1499060615695&h=21b79278\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170703/s00007/1499060615695</a>"},{"pid":"41e17ac2fdbf6834a9ff784723c08bf506900a60","tid":307144,"uid":68094,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecefda3595c7db30a8309c184ce704fc73d328a3","tid":307144,"uid":38172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"左邊定右邊果個先係鄧達智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7cc3c3759064734e667341ef66